 und umfassenden Rechtsrat für die vielfältigen Fragen der arbeitsrechtlichen Praxis.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 4aArbeitsrecht. 7aLAW / Labor & Employment.2bisacsh1 aBittner, Claudia, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aClemenz, Susanne, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aDzida, Boris, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aFischer, Benno Alexander, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aGaul, Björn, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aGeißler, Karl, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aGiesen, Richard, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aGäntgen, Hans Jörg, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aHenssler, Martin, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aHergenröder, Carmen Silvia, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aHergenröder, Curt Wolfgang, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aHohenstatt, Klaus-Stefan, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aHöpfner, Clemens, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aKalb, Heinz-Jürgen, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aKalb, Heinz-Jürgen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKliemt, Michael, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aKlug, Saskia, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aKrause, Rüdiger, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aLembke, Mark, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aMolkenbur, Josef, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aMüller-Bonanni, Thomas, eauthor.4aut4http://id.lo